The Mind of a Chef - Season 3, Episode 5




Kentucky

The Bluegrass State offers so much more than just mint juleps and the Kentucky Derby, with a rich culinary history that rivals that of America's more well-known food destinations. A few ingredients come to Chef Ed Lee's mind when he thinks about his adopted state: country ham, sorghum and smoke
